  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE \"MODEL MISSISSIPPI HAIR PROTECTION IN SCHOOLS POLICY ACT\"; TO REQUIRE PUBLIC AND CHARTER SCHOOLS TO CREATE POLICIES WITH GUIDELINES THAT PROHIBIT DISCRIMINATION BASED ON HAIRSTYLES; TO ESTABLISH MINIMUM GUIDELINES FOR THE POLICIES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
